CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: " Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...9. Riecks Dairy Company, makers of Sealtest milk and dairy Products, made a beautiful addition to the fair with their "Wishing Well" display. Represented by Kenneth Haney and Miss Eunice Brown...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Kenneth Haney and Eunice Brown standing in Sealtest Dairy booth in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
